ration of the\nrelay wherein the relay switches from the receive to the transmit mode based on\nthe source-relay channel quality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2010 05:21:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-08-10"}
