building hybrid density-functional/wavefunction methodology for\nincorporating aspects of nonlocality in time not present in the AA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2010 10:13:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2015 18:14:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
